The Borrowers;;1997;;PG;;Adventure,Comedy,Family;;5.9;;Peter Hewitt;;John Goodman,Jim Broadbent,Mark Williams,Celia Imrie,Flora Newbigin,Tom Felton,Raymond Pickard,Bradley Pierce,Aden Gillett,Doon Mackichan,Hugh Laurie,Ruby Wax,Andrew Dunford,Bob Goody,Patrick Monckton,Dick Ward,George Antoni,Alex Winter;;The Borrowers are four-inch high "little people" who live under the floorboards. When the owner of the house they live in dies and her evil lawyer Ocious P. Potter wants to destroy the house to build luxury apartments in its place, they start to fight him with the help of the son of house owner, Pete.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0118755/